      public EventResponse​(String associatedUsername, String eventId, String personId, float latitude, float longitude, String country, String city, String eventType, int year)
      Creates an event response object
      Parameters:
      associatedUsername - the username of the user account
      eventId - the event's id
      personId - the id of the person who owns this event
      latitude - the event's latitude
      longitude - the event's longitude
      country - the event's country
      city - the event's city
      eventType - the event's type
      year - the event's year
